Camp fees: $60 - 70

The ultimate heist is back and it's bigger than ever before! 💰🔥 Get ready for 4 days of non-stop thrill with your gang, turning SoC into the perfect hideout 🥳🏰 Get ready for the second but the best SoC camp!! 🏦💥

📣 Hey Freshies 
 
Missed out on FSC sign ups❓No worries, we got your back ❤️ Keep a lookout for these events happening soon 🚨🚨🚨 SIGN UP FORMS WILL DROP ANY MOMENT ❗❗❗ 
 
1️⃣ Freshmen Orientation Week (FOW) 
FOW is back and better than ever before! Get ready for 4 days of non-stop fun with new friends that will make SoC feel like home 🥺🏠 Get pumped for the second SoC camp!! HEARSAY GOT BEACH FINALE 🤔‼️drop @kenzverylayz @xintiaann @Brb_bryy a text for any further qns
Camp Dates: 26th-29th July 

 
2️⃣ Freshmen Finale Camp (FFC) 
Yet to join an Orientation Camp?! 🤯 Be a part of SoC's FINAL PHYSICAL camp held in August, right before school starts for you to relax and make friends before the real grind starts 🥵 Burning questions regarding FFC? Slide into our DMs on Telegram @justinsohhh @sziyingg @PapaTaco

[FRESHMEN SOCIAL CAMP 2023 #FSC2023]

HELLO FRESHIES!! Signups for our waitlist have officially closed. 

Due to constraints on our end, we will not be sending out confirmation emails unless you have been selected.

D-7 to FSC ⚡⚡⚡

Calling all freshmen! 📢 It's that time of year again! Join us on FLAG Day and Beneficiary Engagement Day (BED) by volunteering your time and making a difference. Sign up today and be a part of something amazing! 🙌🌟  
 
FLAG Day ✨ 
Sign up with your friends for a fun and meaningful day to give back to society! 
Date🗓️: 29 July, 9am - 5pm 
Location📍: Buona Vista/ Harbourfront/ Jurong East 
 
Beneficiary Engagement Day ✨ 
Conduct beneficiary coding and designing of Canva workshops and meet your fellow SOC-ers while interacting with students with intellectual disabilities of Fernvale Gardens’ School (FGS)! We’re hosting 2 separate engagement days, so feel free to sign up on the day you’re available! 
Date🗓️: 18 / 20 July 2023 730am - 530pm
Location 📍: Fernvale Gardens’ School

Do take note that no transport will be provided for both events, but did we mention that refreshments will be? 🙌🙌 Wait no more, and sign up now at 
https://nus.campuslabs.com/engage/submitter/form/start/593188

See you there!

[FRESHMEN SOCIAL CAMP 2023 #FSC2023]

D-13 to the SoC’s FIRST AND BEST camp FSC!

Thank you so much for your overwhelming support! We will be opening limited slots for waitlist, so do get your friends who missed out to sign up NOW!
https://nus.campuslabs.com/engage/submitter/form/start/594927
Confirmation and waitlist email will be sent out today and tomorrow.

PS. heard the ticket prices DROPPED? anything for u freshies. 🥸

For any additional queries regarding the Camp, do reach out to @danielwang_wk 😎 @tallkoh 👨‍🦳@yushiorsth 👨‍🦰! SEE YA'LL REAL SOON ⚡⚡⚡

The School of Computing is thrilled to announce our first-ever FLAG carnival, and you're all cordially invited! 💻🎪

WHEN 📅: 12th August, from 11am to 2pm
WHERE📍: UTown Green

Treat yourself to our sweet Burnt Cones gelato, and spice things up with henna tattoo artistry at our booth! 🥳🥨🎨 All proceeds from our booth will be channeled to support our beneficiary, making every bite and every stroke a step towards making a difference!

Join us in creating memories, good vibes, and positive impact! We can't wait to see you there 😃🙌🎉

messages.message:
🌟 Welcome to NUS School of Computing (SoC)! 🌟

We are thrilled to have you join our vibrant and innovative community at SoC! As you embark on this exciting journey of knowledge and discovery, we have lined up a series of enriching camps to kickstart your university life. Get ready to forge lasting friendships, and dive into the world of computing! 🤩

1️⃣ Freshmen Social Camp (FSC)
As SoC’s first summer camp, FSC wants to create an environment for you to forge meaningful relationships through 4 days of PHYSICAL fun! The streets are saying there is a huge beach day too? 🥰
Camp Dates: 21st-24th June

2️⃣ Freshmen Orientation Week (FOW)
FOW is back and better than ever before! Get ready for 4 days of non-stop fun with new friends that will make SoC feel like home 🥺🏠 Get pumped for the second SoC camp!! HEARSAY GOT BEACH DAY 🤔‼️
Camp Dates: 26th-29th July

3️⃣ Freshmen Finale Camp (FFC)
FFC is SoC's FINAL PHYSICAL camp held in August, just before school starts for you to relax and make friends before the real grind starts! 🎢👏🏼
Camp Dates: 7th, 8th, 10th August 

4️⃣ SoC Bash 
Bash is SoC’s biggest annual party where SoC’s TOP CHAIS 🥵 come together to put up a spectacular performance! Look forward to a long night of games 🎯, live band 🎸 and MORE ✨
Dates: TBC

Do stay tuned for more detailed information and registration instructions. Participating in these camps will be an excellent opportunity for you to engage with your fellow freshmen, and faculty members.

Remember to get your fellow SoC friends to join our tele channel https://t.me/socfreshmen2324 for regular updates, announcements, and a platform to connect with your batchmates. Do also follow us on Instagram @socfop for more updates. SEE YOU SOON! 🥳 

Best regards,
Freshmen Orientation Programmes (FOP) 💙
